#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:1
msgid "E4168"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `error_poly_unsupported`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:5
msgid "Error polymorphism is not supported in this position."
msgstr "此位置不支持错误多态。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:7
msgid ""
"The `raise?` annotation means that a function is error-polymorphic: it "
"can propagate the error behavior of a callback or another polymorphic "
"operation. MoonBit only supports this form in specific function "
"positions. It is not a general-purpose type annotation that can be used "
"anywhere a function type is written."
msgstr ""
"`raise?` 标注表示函数具有错误多态：它可以传播回调或其他多态操作的错误行为。MoonBit "
"只在特定的函数位置支持这种形式。它不是一个可以在任意函数类型处使用的通用类型标注。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:13
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:15
msgid "The following toplevel value uses `raise?` in a function type annotation:"
msgstr "下面的顶层值在函数类型标注中使用了 `raise?`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:17
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"let _callback : () -> Unit raise? = fn() { () }\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:21
msgid "MoonBit will report an error."
msgstr "MoonBit 会报告一个错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:23
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:25
msgid ""
"Use a non-raising function type when the callback cannot raise, or use an"
" ordinary concrete `raise` annotation in a supported function declaration"
" when the function may raise:"
msgstr "当回调不会抛出错误时，使用不抛错的函数类型；如果函数可能抛错，则在受支持的函数声明中使用普通的具体 `raise` 标注："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4168.md:29
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"let _callback : () -> Unit = fn() { () }\n"
msgstr ""

